  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects will be adult allogeneic HSCT recipients aged â‰¥ 18 years-old (or as
             applicable, per local law) who were CMV seropositive before transplantation and are
             CMV viremia negative posttransplant.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who have a positive CMV viremia test at any time between transplant and the
             First Dose Day (FDD).

          -  Subjects with hypersensitivity (not renal dysfunction or eye disorder) to CDV or to
             CMX001 or its excipients.

          -  Subjects who have received any anti-CMV therapy and investigational anti-CMV drugs at
             any time posttransplant.

          -  Subjects who have had any anti-CMV vaccine at any time.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
